title: Fantasy Book v3#3 (#13) 1984-09
description:
Fantasy Book Vol. 3 No. 3 (whole issue 13), September 1984.

This magazine is a fantasy and science fiction anthology (ISSN 0277-0717) edited by Dennis Mallonee, Nick Smith, and Jessica Salmonson which I have reproduced here as an OCR'd PDF. Contents:

Brunet, James: A Pennant from the Gremlin
Friesner, Esther M.: The Shield-Maiden's Honeymoon
Howard, Robert E.: Skulls
Keller, Gottfried: A Little Legend of the Dance
Lumley, Brian: The Deep Awaits (Part Three of The Return of the Deep Ones)
Schweitzer, Darrell: The Diminishing Man, Part I
Tymon, Steve: The Game of Assassins
Van Hise, James: Demon Wizard
Williamson, J. N.: Milestones
Zimmer, Paul Edwin: The Wolves of Sarlow
